### Retrieve Disbursement Information

This endpoint retrieves information about a specific disbursement with the provided ID.

#### Request

No request body is required for this request.

#### Response

The response will be a JSON object with the following schema:

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "status": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "code": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "data": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "status": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "foreignId": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "transactionId": {
          "type": "string"
        }
      }
    }
  }
}

 ```

### Request Headers

- Content-Type: `multipart/form-data`


### Request Body

- channel (text, required): The channel through which the disbursement will be made.

- mobileWalletNumber (text, required if channel = mobile_wallet): The mobile wallet number of the beneficiary.

- mobileWalletProviderCode (text, required if channel = mobile_wallet): The provider code of the mobile wallet.

- countryCode (text, required): The country code of the beneficiary.


### Response

The response of this request can be represented as a JSON schema:

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "status": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "code": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "data": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "nameOnAccount": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "mobileWalletProvider": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "bankName": {
          "type": "string"
        }
      }
    }
  }
}

 ```

#### Request Body

- `channel` (string, required): The channel through which the disbursement will be made.

- `mobileWalletNumber` (string, required if channel = mobile_wallet): The mobile wallet number of the beneficiary.

- `mobileWalletProviderCode` (string, required if channel = mobile_wallet): The provider code of the mobile wallet.

- `bankAccountNumber` (string, required if channel = bank): The bank number of the beneficiary.

- `bankCode` (string, required if channel = bank): The bank code of the bank.

- `countryCode` (string, required): The country code of the beneficiary.


#### Response

The response of this request can be represented as a JSON schema:

``` json
{
  "type": "object",
  "properties": {
    "status": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "code": {
      "type": "string"
    },
    "data": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "nameOnAccount": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "mobileWalletProvider": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "bankName": {
          "type": "string"
        }
      }
    }
  }
}

 ```

